---
source: crates/tirith/tests/help_snapshots.rs
expression: stdout.to_string()
---
Manage trusted patterns (allowlist entries with TTL, scoping, and audit)

Usage: tirith trust <COMMAND>

Commands:
  add     Add a trusted pattern
  list    List trusted patterns from all sources
  remove  Remove a trusted pattern
  last    Show last trigger and interactively trust domains
  gc      Remove expired entries from trust stores
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help

Examples:
  tirith trust add example.com
  tirith trust add example.com --ttl 7d
  tirith trust list --format json --expired
  tirith trust remove example.com
  tirith trust last
  tirith trust gc
